Package neqsim.fluidmechanics.util.timeseries

Class TimeSeries

java.lang.Object
neqsim.fluidmechanics.util.timeseries.TimeSeries
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class TimeSeries extends Object implements Serializable

TimeSeries class for managing time-varying boundary conditions in transient pipe flow simulations.

This class supports three types of outlet boundary conditions:

  • TimeSeries.OutletBoundaryType.PRESSURE - Specified outlet pressure (default)
  • TimeSeries.OutletBoundaryType.FLOW - Specified outlet flow rate/velocity
  • TimeSeries.OutletBoundaryType.CLOSED - Zero flow at outlet (blocked pipe)
